channel.title: Help, can't put shops and other stuff!
channel.description: I was planning on doing a Varrock Fountain Market, but i can't!!!! So, i was seeing tutorials but they say that you need a client.java file, but i DON'T have that file!!! How's possible to do a hybridscape server for myself?? if it doesn't have client.java? i want to put LOTS of things in... but i cant because i've searched everywhere in my source (every folder), but i dont find the HELL of client.java!!!!! i've put to show hiden files and NOTHING! used search... nothing!!! HELP! oh i almost forgot my version is Moparscape 3.2 w/Aryan.
